query:
SELECT m.id FROM metadata AS m
               JOIN buckets AS b ON m.bucket_id = b.id
               LEFT JOIN snapshots AS s ON s.metadata_id = m.id
               WHERE b.user_id = $1
                   AND b.id = $2
                   AND m.id = $3
                   AND m.state != 'deleted'
                   AND s.id IS NULL;
